// failed-login-timeline.kql
// Purpose: Visualize the attack progression over time in 5-minute buckets
// Use case: Determine whether the attack was sustained or pulsed — indicates automated tooling
// Investigation step: Run after identifying the attacking IP to analyze attack behavior
// Visualization: Render as time chart in Sentinel

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4625
| summarize Attempts = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
| sort by TimeGenerated asc
